out the measurements from such malfunctioning meters was the
original objective of the legacy bad data processing and is still
in practice today [17].
Even though the model in (1) is nonlinear, the state estimate
is generally obtained by iterations of weighted linear
least squares estimation with the locally linearized model [21].
